22:35.809 --> 22:38.412
And in every other way, we are uncomfortable as possible.

22:39.594 --> 22:42.237
A certain percentage of us get killed or imprisoned.

22:43.859 --> 22:45.361
We live in virtual poverty.

22:46.523 --> 22:51.890
We turn back to the party every penny we make above what is absolutely necessary to keep us alive.

22:52.866 --> 23:00.697
We communists don't have the time or the money for many movies or concerts or T-bone sticks or decent homes or new cars.

23:01.538 --> 23:03.020
We've been described as fanatics.

23:04.462 --> 23:05.884
We are fanatics.

23:07.165 --> 23:16.077
Our lives are dominated by one great overshadowing factor, the struggle for world communism.

23:16.097 --> 23:19.622
We communists have a philosophy of life which no amount of money could buy.

23:20.804 --> 23:22.546
We have a cause to fight for.

23:23.138 --> 23:25.480
a definite purpose in life.

23:25.500 --> 23:46.480
We subordinate our petty personal selves into a great movement of humanity, and if our personal lives seem hard or our egos appear to suffer through subordination to the party, then we are adequately compensated by the thought that each of us in a small way is contributing to something new and true and better for mankind.

23:48.081 --> 23:52.946
There is one thing in which I am dead earnest, and that is the Communist cause.

23:53.730 --> 24:04.248
It is my life, my business, my religion, my hobby, my sweetheart, my wife, unmistress, my bread and meat.

24:04.749 --> 24:07.694
I work at it in the daytime and dream of it at night.

24:08.155 --> 24:11.822
It holds me, grows on me, not lessons as time goes on.

24:12.082 --> 24:18.994
Therefore, I cannot carry on a friendship, a love affair, or even a conversation.

24:19.266 --> 24:24.132
without relieving it to this force which both drives and guides my life.

24:24.673 --> 24:33.525
I evaluate people, books, ideas and actions according to how they affect the communist cause and by their attitude toward it.

24:33.985 --> 24:44.719
I've already been in jail because of my ideas and if necessary, I'm ready to go before a firing squad.

24:44.740 --> 24:46.642
He was a fool for communism.

24:48.770 --> 24:55.040
And they're all sorts of fools for all sorts of isms on our streets tonight.

25:00.209 --> 25:15.634
But it's because they're not compelled, constrained, captivated by the love of the one who died for us.

25:18.178 --> 25:19.940
And rose again for all.

25:25.888 --> 25:27.009
Will you be a fool for him?

25:31.555 --> 25:32.636
We sang it tonight.

25:34.058 --> 25:36.561
You open my eyes to your wonders and you.

25:38.524 --> 25:42.509
You captured my heart with this love.

25:44.471 --> 25:46.514
Because nothing on earth is as pure

25:49.762 --> 25:50.884
That's it.

25:50.904 --> 25:51.504
That's it.

25:53.467 --> 25:54.028
That's it.

25:55.430 --> 25:56.531
There is nothing else.

26:01.959 --> 26:03.781
Have you been captivated by him?

26:05.864 --> 26:16.338
And as you go, or will you go with that compulsion driven by the love, nothing else?

26:20.066 --> 26:21.448
Now we're going to have permanency.

26:23.610 --> 26:26.974
I'm going to pray briefly for you now, but we're going to permanency.

26:26.994 --> 26:35.965
And I want to invite you, if you have other loves, there's a word for that called idols.

26:38.008 --> 26:49.522
If you need to deal with those other loves, they could be very overtly sinful things, or they could be legitimate things, but they're taken up a place in your heart that you know

26:50.242 --> 26:51.223
belongs to Jesus.

26:52.865 --> 27:02.133
But if you need a little bit of help and someone to stand with you tonight to confess that and to deal with it, there's a prayer team that's going to be up here coming.

27:02.834 --> 27:10.281
But then as you empty yourself of that idol, and maybe even take up your cross and say, I am to myself of myself.

27:10.722 --> 27:13.044
Because listen, I am a coward, OK?

27:13.404 --> 27:15.947
I'm not CT stud, right?

27:15.967 --> 27:16.627
I'm no stud.

27:17.728 --> 27:19.410
You know?

27:20.674 --> 27:21.755
I need help with this.

27:21.916 --> 27:25.240
I let my comforts, you know?

27:25.260 --> 27:26.522
I don't like danger.

27:29.025 --> 27:41.522
I've struggled with fear in my lifetime and still could, but I know that the love of Jesus Christ will overwhelm anything.

27:42.466 --> 27:49.195
And I know that my answer and my secret is being filled with him to push all those other things out.

27:49.515 --> 28:06.937
So if you want not just to be emptied of your idols, your sin and yourself, but you want to be captivated and filled, immersed, submerged, overwhelmed by the love of Christ, as we worship, the prayer team will be up here and there's an opportunity to pray over you.

28:09.781 --> 28:10.482
Will you do that?

28:11.330 --> 28:22.065
In order that you can go with this love, I'll tell you, you can have the ABC of the gospel, you can know your theology.

28:22.766 --> 28:25.069
You can be okay with the gifts of the Spirit.

28:25.229 --> 28:33.460
I'm telling you now that if you've got love, the love of Christ dressing on you, you will be a walking revival.

28:33.480 --> 28:37.846
It's a thing people are crying out for is love, more than anything.

28:39.228 --> 28:40.850
Lord, I want to thank you.

28:42.242 --> 28:46.047
For your word, I thank you for your love.

28:47.649 --> 28:51.174
I thank you for Jesus who's shown us your love.

28:51.835 --> 28:52.896
Demonstrated it.

28:53.417 --> 28:54.959
They're why we were still sinners.

28:55.059 --> 28:56.261
Christ died for us.

28:56.942 --> 29:01.748
And Lord, we invite you Holy Spirit to come and rest on people.

29:03.230 --> 29:09.138
I pray that you will rest from their grasp those idols that they are holding on to.

29:09.858 --> 29:11.540
rest from their grasp.

29:11.820 --> 29:14.082
Help them, Lord, to let go.

29:14.863 --> 29:16.345
Take them from them.

29:16.385 --> 29:26.775
Help them to lay down their lives for you as an offering.

29:28.177 --> 29:35.184
And take up the cross tonight and doing that as you cleanse them as a vessel and they're emptying themselves.

29:35.624 --> 29:37.426
Lord, would you fill them?

29:37.762 --> 29:48.095
with the supernatural agape love of heaven, the love of God, that is four-dimensional, incomprehensible.

29:49.637 --> 29:58.007
Would you fill them with the Holy Spirit and your love and send them out, compelled by the love of Jesus?

29:59.849 --> 30:00.690
In whose name we pray?

